<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>{% block title %}{{ 'menu.graduate' | trans }} {% endblock %}</title>
  {{ include('_head.html.twig') }}
  {% block css %}{% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
<div class="all-wrapper container-fluid">
  {% include '_banner_top.html.twig' %}
  <div class="layout-w ">
    <div class="content-w infos_rgpd">
      <div class="element-wrapper">
        <div class="content-box">
          <div class="element-box">
            <p>The information collected on this form is recorded in a centralized and secure database by the Institut de la Francophonie pour l'éducation et la formation (IFEF), located in Dakar, Senegal
              (person in charge: Mrs Léna WATT, <mailto:lena.watt@francophonie.org> lena.watt@francophonie.org), in order to measure the integration rate of technical education and vocational training graduates.
            </p>
            <p>The data collected will be communicated only to the users of the application, except for the data from the questionnaires, which remain confidential and are only used for general statistics.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="element-wrapper">
        <div class="content-box">
          <div class="element-box">
            <p>The data is kept for a maximum period of 5 years by the data controller.
              You can access the data concerning you, rectify them, delete them at any time by editing your account.
            </p>
            <p>You can also withdraw your consent at any time or object to the processing of your data.
              You can also exercise your right to the portability of your data.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="element-wrapper">
        <div class="content-box">
          <div class="element-box">
            <p>To exercise these rights or for any questions about the processing of your data in this device, you can contact, if necessary, the person in charge of the protection of this data:
              (Ms Léna WATT, <mailto:lena.watt@francophonie.org> lena.watt@francophonie.org, tel. + 221 33 859 25 53, IFEF, PO Box 29437, Dakar-Yoff, CP 12000, Dakar, Senegal) .
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
